{
  "stem": "24242.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to Naliboki Pushcha, it was already endless woods, endless swamps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, somewhere, somehow, it got to the, to the Germans that there is a lot of partisans in the Naliboki Pushcha.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they decided to eliminate ours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to leave the camp and run deeper into the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to cross swamps and then find a little island again [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on a drier spot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is how we survived the attack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They attacked us, I think, for about a week or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it stands in my eyes like, like yesterday, how the-- their artillery, their, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I guess, small missiles or the bullets of the artillery, they were flying over our head.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or they will, they would fall ahead of us or behind us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some way, somehow, we had no casualties by pure luck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Nazis were very mechanized, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very clean dressed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They would not want to get dirty, I guess, in the swamps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or they were somewhat afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they would, would not get off the main road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is the way we survived until the Russian army came in 1940-- middle of 1944--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liberated us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you had, you had horse and buggies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it's in the winter, you have, you have horses and sleds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever you had to take on the sled, you put on the sled, or on the buggy if it's in the summer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this attack happened to be in the summer, was not winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All you do is carry your, carry your rifle, your armament.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You leave everything else.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
